name: Dark Brown Pencil
description:
Dark Brown Pencil with built in sharpener - great for eyes and brows!

Ingredients & Directions

Sharpen or dull your liner pencil if necessary. The sharpness of your eyeliner pencil will affect the way that the eyeliner looks. You can create a precise, thin line by sharpening your pencil, or you can create a more rounded, thick line by dulling the pencil.

Ceresin, Cera Carnuba, Synthetic Beeswax, Caprylic/Capric Triglyceride, Isoprolyl Palmitate, Lanolin, Parrafin Oils, Cyanocobalamin. May Contain: , CI 77499 (Iron Oxides), May Contain [+/-]: Mica (CI 77019), Titanium Dioxide (CI 77891), Bismuth Oxychloride (CI 77163), Iron Oxides (CI 77491, CI 77492, CI 77499), Manganese Violet (CI 77742), Carmine (CI 75470), Red 28 (CI 45410), Blue 1 (CI 42090), Yellow 5 (CI 19140), Red 7 (CI 15850), Red 6 (CI 15850), Red 21 (CI 45380), Red 30 (CI 73360).

Who Should Use Eye Pencil

Everyone looking a sharp look for their gorgeous eyes.

*Not made in USA*

name: White Eye Pencil
description:
Now you can make your eyes pop and look bigger and brighter! To make your eyes appear larger apply to your lower eyeline and waterline. Apply above your lash line to make them even larger. To brighten your eyes and make them look less red, apply to the inner corner of your eyes and smudge it on. To lift your brows apply it and rub it in under your eyebrows. To make your lashes look fuller apply on your upper lash line. There are a plethora of white eye pencil videos on YouTube we suggest you check out to maximize your new cosmetic favorite!

Ingredients & Directions

Sharpen or dull your liner pencil if necessary. The sharpness of your eyeliner pencil will affect the way that the eyeliner looks. You can create a precise, thin line by sharpening your pencil, or you can create a more rounded, thick line by dulling the pencil.

name: Easy on the Eyes
description:
We are so elated to now offer an eye makeup remover. We have been perfecting this formula in our beauty lab for a very long time and we have finally nailed it! It is incredibly gentle, so it is perfect for sensitive eyes and contact lens wearers. Our formula doesn’t leave an oily residue, so eye makeup applies without smearing!
*Bonus feature - have fun ‘shaking it up’ before each use!

Ingredients & Directions

Directions: Shake the product well until the two parts are mixed. Lightly squeeze product onto a face towel or cotton round and gently rub all over the face until makeup is completely removed.

Ingredients: Water, Cyclopentasiloxane, Poloxamer 184, Butylene Glycol, Cucumis Sativus (Cucumber) Fruit Extract, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice, Benzyl Alcohol, Sodium Chloride, Allantoin, Glycerin, Benzalkonium Chloride, Disodium EDTA, Potassium Phosphate, Dipotassium Phosphate
